1.1 Revenge Trade TanÄ±mÄ±
Revenge Trade:
â”œâ”€ Son trade kayÄ±p
â”œâ”€ Hemen telafi etme dÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼ncesi
â”œâ”€ Aceleci, dÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼ncesiz entry
â”œâ”€ Genelde daha bÃ¼yÃ¼k kayÄ±p
â””â”€ Emotional decision (logic deÄŸil)

Neden Tehlikeli:
â”œâ”€ Standartlar dÃ¼ÅŸÃ¼yor
â”œâ”€ Risk artÄ±yor
â”œâ”€ FOMO ile birleÅŸiyor
â””â”€ Spiral (loss â†’ revenge â†’ loss â†’ revenge...)
1.2 Coin-Based Cooldown System
COOLDOWN_RULES = {
    
    # â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
